          documentation for the package being built.</para>
          <indexterm zone="gtk-doc gtkdoc">
            <primary sortas="b-gtkdoc*">gtkdoc*</primary>
          </indexterm>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

    </variablelist>

  </sect2>

